<div id="gs-profile-signup" class="section">
  <h2>Sign Up</h2>
  <p>
    You must sign up in order to post to a group or receive email when
    someone posts to a group.
    Signing up is a four-step process. 
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-email">Enter an email address</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-password">Set a password</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-profile">Change your profile</a></li>
    <li><a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify your email
      address</a></li>
  </ol>
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-email" class="section">
    <h3>Enter Email</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Click the <samp class="button">Sign up</samp> button.
        An email message will be sent to you, verifying that you control
        the address you entered.
        You will be taken to the 
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-password">Set Password</a> page.</li>
    </ol>
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-email-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-password" class="section">
    <h3>Set Password</h3>
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-password-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-profile" class="section">
    <h3>Change Profile</h3>    
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-profile-->
  <div id="gs-profile-signup-verify" class="section">
    <h3>Verify Email</h3>
    <p>
      To verify your email address
    </p>
    <ol>
      <li>Check your email. 
        It should contain a message asking you to verify the
        address.
        If it does not go through the procedures in 
        <a href="#gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble">Trouble Shooting</a>
        below.</li>
      <li>Click the link in the email. 
        You will be taken to the <cite class="page">Address 
          Verified</cite> page.</li>
      <li>Close the <cite class="page">Address Verified</cite> page.</li>
      <li>Find the window showing the 
        <cite class="page">Awaiting Verification</cite> page.
        The <samp class="button">Finish</samp> button on the page will
        be available.</li>
      <li>
        Click on the <samp class="button">Finish</samp> button to finish
        sign up.
        You will be taken to&#8230;
      </li>
    </ol>
    <div id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble" class="section">
      <h4>Trouble Shooting</h4>
      <p>
        If your email does not contain a message asking you to verify
        your address carry out the following tasks. 
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-junk">Check the
          <samp>Junk</samp> folder in your email to see if the message
          is there.
          If it is then you should go carry out steps 2&#8213;5 in the 
          <a href="gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify Email</a> section 
          above.</li><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-junk-->
        <li id="gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-correct">Check that
          your email address is correct.
          If the address is incorrect
          <ol>
            <li>Enter a new address in the
              <samp class="entry">Email Address</samp> entry.</li>
            <li>Click the
              <samp class="entry">Send</samp> button.
              A new verification email will be sent to you.</li>
            <li>Carry out the steps in the
              <a href="gs-profile-signup-verify">Verify Email</a> section 
              above.</li>
          </ol>
        </li><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-correct-->
      </ol>
    </div><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-trouble-->
  </div><!--gs-profile-signup-verify-->
</div><!--gs-profile-signup-->

